- Range Trooper Cuirass, Fur Pauldrons and Helmet
- Imperial Jumpsuit
- Imperial Gunner Helmet</text>
			</li>
			<li>
				<header>New Troopers</header>
				<text>There are now several new trooper types!
- Snow Troopers - will show up in raids on maps with cold climates.
- Death Troopers - can show up in raids and Imperial settlements, or with traders.
- Range Troopers - can show up in raids (cold and temperate only) and Imperial settlements.
- Imperial Gunners - Only seen in Imperial settlements.

These are of course all using the appropriate new equipment.</text>
			</li>
