				<header>Fixes</header>
				<text>- Imperial Officers and Traders now spawn with a temperature regulator so they can better survive extreme cold/hot climates.
- If you have Droid Depot, KX-Series droids will now spawn in Galactic Empire settlements.
- ISB Training now enhances more social stats, with the combat training being more minimal.</text>
			</li>
